{"tid":1885663,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北韓發現第一起武漢肺炎確診病例，南韓媒體爆料該確診者已槍斃","createTime":"2020-02-18T12:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T02:52:55.000Z","uid":28114,"like":677,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee30193f1271ec65e1b7c2c064d1df008506414","tid":1885663,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/excerpt_images/76277/original/aa4bc8b597b8078578f4482d09058b38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fexcerpt_images%2F76277%2Foriginal%2Faa4bc8b597b8078578f4482d09058b38.jpg&h=df16b0d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情延燒全球，雖然北韓鄰近中國，但是北韓早在1月22就宣布關閉邊境，再加上封閉式的管理，因此北韓一再表示並沒有武漢肺炎的確診病例。不過，根據南韓媒體的報導，在北韓邊境的新義州市已出現首例確診病例，並且當局已經下令將新義州市「封城」，而南韓媒體表示，該名病例可能已經被槍斃。<br />\n<br />\n根據《東亞日報》報導表示，由於北韓的醫療資源有限，為了防止武漢肺炎病毒的入侵，他們其實以相當高規格的方式來防疫。包括經由中國遼寧入境到北韓的人，隔離的期間長達一個月、停飛所有往返中國的火車以及班機。另外，也在中國的醫療單位協助下取得了檢驗試劑，因此平壤友誼醫院也有檢驗病毒的能力。<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓朝鮮日報的報導，則指出北韓的新義州市已經有兩起武漢肺炎的疑似病例，其中有一起確診病例。而為什麼新義州市會出現病例，主要是因為位於中國與北韓邊境的新義州市，有走私活動在進行。<br />\n<br />\n而這次傳出被感染武漢肺炎確診病例的患者，傳就是在當地走私礦物規模最大的貿易公司工作，為碼頭的管理員。而這名病患之所以會被傳染，被推斷可能是在北韓下令關閉邊境後，繼續前往中國走私才會染病。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/545961/original/416f272b9bfeafabfb5b58891ae77c22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F545961%2Foriginal%2F416f272b9bfeafabfb5b58891ae77c22.jpg&h=53cc7ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而根據南韓媒體推測，由於該名病患違反禁令，預料將會依照軍法處置，可能已經被直接處決。而新義州市當地的負責官員，也因為防疫不力而遭免職。<br />\n<br />\n由於北韓對於武漢肺炎防疫的醫療能力不足，為了預防武漢肺炎在當地大規模擴散，北韓是全球第一個因為疫情而將所有邊界封閉的國家，金正恩也已經取消了每年春季的軍事閱兵活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/76277-north-korea-finds-first-confirmed-case-of-wuhan-pneumonia-south-korean-media-say-the-confirmed-man-has-been-shot?from=home_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F76277-north-korea-finds-first-confirmed-case-of-wuhan-pneumonia-south-korean-media-say-the-confirmed-man-has-been-shot%3Ffrom%3Dhome_news&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=1bfc3a65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/76277-north-korea-finds-first-confirmed-case-of-wuhan-pneumonia-south-korean-media-say-the-confirmed-man-has-been-shot?from=home_news</a>"},{"pid":"95c96c061672af6798b1a0115aa3c60d7c283f04","tid":1885663,"uid":28114,"like":376,"dislike":2,"score":374,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"北韓又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b941832e4e2fe39e448281a3611697295bb4c55f","tid":1885663,"uid":88743,"like":604,"dislike":4,"score":600,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"確診人數 1<br />\n痊癒人數 1"},{"pid":"c4ac1d1dc463291c908709218b80acc527ac9504","tid":1885663,"uid":12609,"like":65,"dislike":4,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"識揀一定揀犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2ef9dac70209c4d9bb017c8c2e3a09dfc5df3c","tid":1885663,"uid":48964,"like":318,"dislike":1,"score":317,"quote":{"pid":"b941832e4e2fe39e448281a3611697295bb4c55f","tid":1885663,"uid":88743,"like":604,"dislike":4,"score":600,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"確診人數 1<br />\n痊癒人數 1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"死亡人數 0 （槍斃唔計）"},{"pid":"e16b87ea6907cc61f228dc7b3ab7bce1d94e2beb","tid":1885663,"uid":123308,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"c4ac1d1dc463291c908709218b80acc527ac9504","tid":1885663,"uid":12609,"like":65,"dislike":4,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"識揀一定揀犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"到時又病毒變種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c334bf338a9070